[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q110 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Chair:[bold] If the valuers decide that it is not value for money, the Government’s policy on relaxing and removing caps on student numbers is totally screwed.
[normal]Mr Willetts[bold]: I 
[normal]don’t 
[normal]think that is an expression you will find in our Government policy document.  We always try to make them more user-friendly, but we 
[normal]haven’t 
[normal]go
[normal]ne
