[normal]these points
[normal].  If graduate repayments are lower because average earnings are lower than forecast, that is different from graduate repayments being lower because the Student Loans Company fails to pursue people efficiently.  We have to disentangle those different effects.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q137 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Caroline Dinenage:[bold] Forgive me
